channel.title: Gmod Machinima
channel.description:
I decided to let this out in the open.
Anyway, yes. I am making a gmod machinima based on the Original Fan Fiction by Zach Archer.
I have done 3 episodes already, And another 23 on the way. None of them have been uploaded yet, But..
I do need help from you guys.
I've had some help already, Thanks to those.
I can't think of a decent name and logo. Like Icton's. That is unique.
Does anyone have any ideas for a name and logo?
All I can do in return at the moment is a block in the credits for every machinima episode.
Thanks. :smiley:
